div.p:
THis hath been the affliction of many Saints, as holy Job that had a wife that would have him curse God and die;

                     And Samson, how unequally yoaked was he.
                   and a Christian may come to be unequally yoaked, either that they may be mistaken, and think they marry in the Lord, and it prove contrary to their expectation; or the Lord may work upon the Husband or the Wife after their coming together; therefore to such as come thus to be unequally yoaked,
